text: The 2025 UEFA Under-19 Futsal Championship qualifying competition will be a men's under-19 futsal competition to determine the seven teams joining the automatically qualified hosts Moldova in the 2025 UEFA Under-19 Futsal Championship final tournament. ==Teams== Apart from Moldova, a total of 35 (out of 54) UEFA member national teams entered the qualifying stage. ===Group A=== ===Group B=== ===Group B=== ==References== Category:UEFA Category:Futsal Category:2025 in sports
title: 2025 UEFA Under-19 Futsal Championship Qualification
